libkiwix
------------------------------------------
The Libkiwix provides the Kiwix software suite core. It contains the code
shared by all Kiwix ports (Windows, GNU/Linux, macOS, Android, iOS, ...).

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.6-1
  libcurl-devel-8.18.0-1
  libcurl4-8.18.0-1
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  libicu-devel-76.1-2
  libicu76-76.1-2
  libkiwix-devel-14.1.1-1bl1
  libkiwix14-14.1.1-1bl1
  libmicrohttpd-devel-1.0.2-1bl1
  libmicrohttpd12-1.0.2-1bl1
  libpugixml1-1.9-1
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1
  libxapian-devel-1.4.30-1
  libxapian30-1.4.30-1
  libzim-devel-9.4.1-1bl1
  libzim9-9.4.1-1bl1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1
  python39-3.9.16-1
  zlib-devel-1.3.1-1
  zlib0-1.3.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  Mustache-4.1-1bl2
  binutils-2.45.1-1
  cygport-0.37.6-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  libcurl-devel-8.18.0-1
  libgtest-devel-1.17.0-1bl1
  libicu-devel-76.1-2
  libmicrohttpd-devel-1.0.2-1bl1
  libpugixml-devel-1.9-1
  libxapian-devel-1.4.30-1
  libzim-devel-9.4.1-1bl1
  meson-1.4.2-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1
  zlib-devel-1.3.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/kiwix/libkiwix

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/kiwix/libkiwix/archive/refs/tags/14.1.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libkiwix-14.1.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libkiwix-14.1.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libkiwix-14.1.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libkiwix-14.1.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libkiwix14-14.1.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libkiwix-devel-14.1.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libkiwix)
  /usr/bin/kiwix-compile-i18n
  /usr/bin/kiwix-compile-resources
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libkiwix.README
  /usr/share/doc/libkiwix/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/libkiwix/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libkiwix/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/libkiwix/README.md
  /usr/share/man/man1/kiwix-compile-i18n.1.gz
  /usr/share/man/man1/kiwix-compile-resources.1.gz

(libkiwix14)
  /usr/bin/cygkiwix-14.dll

(libkiwix-devel)
  /usr/include/kiwix/book.h
  /usr/include/kiwix/bookmark.h
  /usr/include/kiwix/common.h
  /usr/include/kiwix/downloader.h
  /usr/include/kiwix/i18n.h
  /usr/include/kiwix/kiwix_config.h
  /usr/include/kiwix/kiwixserve.h
  /usr/include/kiwix/library.h
  /usr/include/kiwix/manager.h
  /usr/include/kiwix/name_mapper.h
  /usr/include/kiwix/search_renderer.h
  /usr/include/kiwix/server.h
  /usr/include/kiwix/spelling_correction.h
  /usr/include/kiwix/tools.h
  /usr/include/kiwix/version.h
  /usr/lib/libkiwix.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libkiwix.pc

